data.description: Introducing 8416 Seth St, nestled in the desirable neighborhood of San Gabriel, CA 91776. This charming fixer upper presents an incredible opportunity to create a dream home tailored to your unique vision. With a bit of TLC  this promising property holds the potential to become a true gem. This property offers ample space with 3 bedrooms/2 bathrooms, and a spacious living area spanning 1,564 square feet.    Whether you're seeking excellent schools, nearby parks, or a vibrant community, this prime location has it all.    Don't miss out on this fantastic investment opportunity in a sought-after neighborhood.    Accepting offers until Monday, November 6, 2023 @ 5pm.
